# Don't touch files outside this repo

This workspace is `/home/thomas/projects/quickshell`. Personal machine config that
this shell integrates with (e.g. `~/.config/niri/`, other dotfiles, systemd units)
lives outside it.

- Do not create, edit, or delete files outside this workspace root — even ones
  directly related to the task (niri config, greetd config, systemd units, etc.).
- Read those files if useful for context or diagnosis.
- Instead of editing them, tell the user exactly what change is needed (a diff or
  the new file contents) and let them apply it themselves.
- Only exception: if the user explicitly asks you to make the edit yourself in
  that specific message (e.g. "go ahead and change my niri config"), you may do so
  for that request.
